        title: "Backdrop blur și transparență",
        content: "Glassmorphism = efect de sticlă frosted. Populat de iOS și macOS design, acum prezent peste tot în web design modern.\n\nBASIC GLASS CARD:\n```html\n<!-- Fundal cu gradient (necesar pentru efect glass) -->\n<div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-700 via-blue-600 to-cyan-500\n            flex items-center justify-center p-8\">\n\n  <!-- Cardul glass -->\n  <div class=\"backdrop-blur-md bg-white/20\n              border border-white/30\n              rounded-2xl p-8\n              shadow-xl shadow-black/20\n              text-white max-w-sm w-full\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2\">Glass Card</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-white/80\">Efect de sticlă frosted cu Tailwind</p>\n    <button class=\"mt-4 w-full py-2 bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30\n                   border border-white/40 rounded-xl\n                   font-medium transition-all\">\n      Acțiune\n    </button>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\nCLASE GLASS în Tailwind:\n- `backdrop-blur-sm/md/lg/xl/2xl/3xl` — blur pe fundal\n- `bg-white/20` — fundal alb cu 20% opacitate\n- `bg-black/10` — fundal negru cu 10% opacitate\n- `border-white/30` — border alb semitransparent\n- `text-white/80` — text alb cu 80% opacitate\n\nVARIANTE GLASS:\n```html\n<!-- Glass întunecat -->\n<div class=\"backdrop-blur-lg bg-black/30 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  Card glass dark\n</div>\n\n<!-- Glass colorat -->\n<div class=\"backdrop-blur-md bg-blue-500/20 border border-blue-400/30 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  Card glass albastru\n</div>\n```",
