        content: "Tailwind CSS @layer permite adăugarea de stiluri custom organizate în straturi.\n\n```css\n/* globals.css sau tailwind.css */\n@tailwind base;\n@tailwind components;\n@tailwind utilities;\n\n/* LAYER BASE — stiluri globale, reset-uri, variabile CSS */\n@layer base {\n  :root {\n    --color-primary: 14 165 233; /* sky-500 în RGB */\n    --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n  }\n  \n  body {\n    @apply font-sans text-gray-900 bg-white;\n  }\n  \n  h1 { @apply text-3xl font-bold; }\n  h2 { @apply text-2xl font-semibold; }\n}\n\n/* LAYER COMPONENTS — componente refolosibile -->\n@layer components {\n  .btn {\n    @apply px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors\n           focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2;\n  }\n  \n  .btn-primary {\n    @apply btn bg-blue-600 text-white hover:bg-blue-700\n           focus:ring-blue-500;\n  }\n  \n  .btn-secondary {\n    @apply btn bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-200\n           focus:ring-gray-400;\n  }\n  \n  .card {\n    @apply bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6;\n  }\n  \n  .input {\n    @apply w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg\n           focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\n           text-gray-900 placeholder-gray-400;\n  }\n}\n\n/* LAYER UTILITIES — utility classes custom */\n@layer utilities {\n  .text-balance {\n    text-wrap: balance;\n  }\n  \n  .no-scrollbar {\n    scrollbar-width: none;\n    -ms-overflow-style: none;\n    &::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\n  }\n}\n```\n\nFOLOSIRE în HTML:\n```html\n<button class=\"btn-primary\">Salvează</button>\n<div class=\"card\">Conținut card</div>\n<input class=\"input\" placeholder=\"Email...\" />\n```",
